data.title: List of Backward Classes Approved TN
data.meta_description: List of Backward ClassesÂ  Approved Tn - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document lists 85 communities designated as backward classes in Tamil Nadu along with their corresponding Sl. No. in the Central OBC list. Some key communities include Agamudayar, Alwar, Ansar, Arayar, Ayira Vaisyar, Badagar, Billava, Boyas, Chakkala, Chettu, Devangar, Dombs, Dudekula, Gounder, Hegde, Illathu Pillaimar, Jogis, Kallar, Kani, Kongu Vellalars, Labbais, Lingayat, Malayar, Maravars, Muthuraja, Nadar, and Naikkar
